QueryResult.text: select odf_scenarios.id odf_pk, ODF_SCENARIOS.ID as scenario_key, ODF_SCENARIOS.ID as clarity_scenario_key, odf_scenarios.NAME as scenario_name, odf_scenarios.CODE as scenario_id, odf_scenarios.DESCRIPTION as description, odf_scenarios.TYPE as object_type, odf_scenarios.ASSOCIATED_OBJECT_ID as object_key, odf_scenarios.IS_PLAN_OF_RECORD as is_plan_of_record, odf_scenarios.IS_BASELINE as is_baseline, odf_scenarios.SRC_SCENARIO_ID as source_scenario_key, ODF_SCENARIOS.CREATED_DATE as clarity_created_date, ODF_SCENARIOS.LAST_UPDATED_DATE as clarity_updated_date from odf_scenarios odf_scenarios where 1 = 1
